OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Outgoing CEO Nick
OL,4,CRead to give evidence
OL,6,FNick Read told ITV News on Wednesday
OL,7,Fthat the public will hear a lot from
OL,8,Fhim over the next three days during
OL,9,Fthe inquiry
OL,11,FOutgoing Post Office boss, Nick Read,
OL,12,Fwill start giving evidence at the
OL,13,Ffinal phase of the Horizon IT inquiry
OL,14,Fon Wednesday.
OL,16,FRead, who is stepping down from his
OL,17,Frole as Chief Executive in March 2025,
OL,18,Fwill give three days of testimony and
OL,19,Fthen face questioning at the inquiry
OL,20,Finto the Post Office scandal.
