OL,3,CPost Office Inquiry: Outgoing CEO Nick
OL,4,CRead to give evidence
OL,6,FHe was brought in to replace former
OL,7,FCEO Paula Vennells in 2019 and "right
OL,8,Fthe wrongs of the past".
OL,10,FHowever, Read has come under heavy
OL,11,Fcriticism throughout the inquiry and
OL,12,Fhas taken several months to prepare
OL,13,Ffor his appearance.
OL,15,FHe says he wants to prove that
OL,16,F"nothing like this can ever happen
OL,17,Fagain."
