OL,6,FAlso, former Post Office chairman
OL,7,FHenry Staunton described Read as
OL,8,F"unstable" on October 1 during the
OL,9,Finquiry, while Read himself listened
OL,10,Ffrom the public gallery.
OL,12,FBetween 1999 and 2015, over 700 Post
OL,13,FOffice sub-postmasters were convicted
OL,14,Fof theft or false accounting and
OL,15,Fthousands more were forced to make up
OL,16,Fshortfalls due to a problem with
OL,17,FFujitsu's Horizon software.
OL,19,FFour suicides were blamed on the
OL,20,Fscandal.
